Rowdy Wolf:






"I'm not sure if that is Predacon territory. I think you're correct, Zyber, 
it doesn't belong to the Predacons. But some lands up here do. See, this 
little scout named Quickstrike travel up here and claimed some territory, 
away from his usual. There's a big land mass belonging to them here. He was 
a good scout. If you ask me, he did a rather good job. He knew how to 
survive. He also turned me into a Predacon. He told me a few things about 
them." He squinted. "Interesting bot, he was."
